Section 3137, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/136/tI/s107"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–136, title I, § 107","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/487/tI/s106"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–487, title I, § 106","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/2332"},"text":"90 Stat. 2332","children":[],"tail":", authorized increase in amount of grant for construction cost increases after grant had been made."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbc724783-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2025—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/272"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–272","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (b) and struck out former subsec. (b). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “To carry out subsection (a), or for any other purpose relating to economic development activities, the Secretary may convene meetings with Federal agencies, State and local governments, economic development districts, Indian tribes, and other appropriate planning and development organizations.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/373"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–373","children":[],"tail":" designated existing provisions as subsec. (a), inserted heading, inserted “Indian tribes,” after “districts,”, and added subsec. (b)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idbc724784-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":